quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Maaku : ""Wahayinaama e am, won'de dental jinna keɗiimo [kam miɗo jannga Alqur'aana], ɗi wi'i: ""Minen min nani janngeteende haawniinde."
  72,2,"Hende ɗowira e peewal. Min ngooŋɗinii nde. Min kafidatah e Joomi amen, hay e gooto."
  72,3,"E won'de manngural Joomi amen ngal mawnii, o siforaali jogitagol genndo, wonaa ɓiɗɗo !"
  72,4,"E won'de [Ibuliisa] ɗayɗo on e amen hino wowlaynoo penaale e hoore Allah."
  72,5,"Minen min cikkuno won'de yimɓe e jinna wowlataano fenaande e hoore Allah."
  72,6,"Hari le worɓe yimɓe hino mooloratnoo worɓe jinna, ɓe ɓesdi ɗi bewre."
  72,7,"Kamɓe [yimɓe ɓeen] ɓe cikkir no sikkirɗon noon, won'de Allah immintintah hay gooto."
  72,8,"E won'de min meemii kammu ngun, min tawi hingu hebbiniraa aynooɓe tiiɗuɓe e docote."
  72,9,"E won'de miɗen njooɗotonoo ton fii keɗagol. Kala non keɗitiiɗo jooni, o hawray e docotal tommbingal."
  72,10,"E won'de min nganndaa si ko bone fa'andanaa wonɓe ka leddi ɓen, kaa hara Joomi maɓɓe faandani ɓe peewal."
  72,11,"E won'de hino e amen moƴƴuɗi, hino e amen kadi ko jaasi ɗum. Hari miɗen e laawi ceertuɗi."
  72,12,"E won'de min pellituno min laawotaako Allah ka hoore leydi, e won'de min laawortaa Mo dogugol."
  72,13,"E won'de nde min nanunoo peewal nagl, min ngooɗini ngal. Kala gooŋɗinɗo Joomi mum, oon hulataa ɗuytaneede [moƴƴi] wonaa ɓeydaneede [bonɗi]."
  72,14,"E won'de hino e amen jebbiliiɗi, hino e amen kadi ooñiiɗi. Kala jebbilii ngii, ɗin ɗoon faandike peewal."
  72,15,"Ooñiiɗi ɗiin kan, ɗi laatanike Jahannama oon carmalle."
  72,16,"E won'de si ɓe ñiiɓuno e hoore laawol ngol, ko pellet, Min njarnayno ɓe ndiyam ɗuuɗuɗam,"
  72,17,"fii yo Min ndaarndoro ɓe heen. Kala ɗuurniiɗo e Jaŋtoore Joomi mum nden, O naaday mo e lepte caɗtuɗe."
  72,18,"E won'de juulirɗe ɗeen ko Allah leeranii. Wata on kafidu e Allah hay e gooto."
  72,19,"E won'de tuma jiyaaɗo Allah on darinoo himo rewa mo, ɗi ɗeɓuno waɗɗondirgol e hoore makko."
  72,20,"Maaku : ""nganndee ko Joomi am (tan) mi ndewata, mi kafidataa mo kadi hay e gooto""."
  72,21,"Maaku : ""Miin mi waawanaa on duñude lorra, wonaa fii pooɗugol nafa""."
  72,22,"Maaku : ""Hay gooto waawaa daɗndugol kam e Allah; mi heɓataa ko woori mo ƴooñorde"
  72,23,"si wonaa yottingol immorde e Allah e nule makko ɗeen. Kala jedduɗo Allah e Nulaaɗo makko on, haray ko Yiite Jahannama woodani mo, ɓe luttay e magge poomaa."
  72,24,"Haa si ɓe nji'ii ko ɓe kammbirananoo kon, ɓe aray anndude ko hombo ɓuri lo'ode ballo, ɓuri kadi famɗude limoore."
  72,25,"Maaku : ""Mi anndaa si ko kammbiranaɗon kon hino ɓadii, maa si koomi am waɗanat ɗuum dumunna."
  72,26,"Ko o ganndo wirniiɗi. O ƴellintinantaa wirniiɗi makko ɗiin hay e gooto."
  72,27,"si wonaa mo o welanaa e Nulaaɗo, o naadnay ye'eso on e ɓaawo makko tommbotooɓe."
  72,28,"fii yo o anndu won'de ɓen njottinii nule joomi maɓɓe ɗeen. O huɓindorii (anndugol) ko woni ka maɓɓe kon, O mofti limoore kala hu'unde""."
